---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Education Solutions | Lovosis">
  <main class="overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509062522246-3755977927d7?ixlib=rb-4.0.3" 
          alt="Education Solutions Hero"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center text-white px-4">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 animate-fade-in">
          Education Solutions
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-fade-in-delayed">
          Impart knowledge in style
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Industry Requirements Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16">Industry Requirements</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Requirement 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="h-16 w-16 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-4">Simplification of Classroom Environment</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">It is necessary to completely solve the pain points such as massive classroom equipment, messy wiring and dust hazards.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Requirement 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="h-16 w-16 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-4">Improvement of Interactive Experience</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">Strengthen the display effect, and combine superior educational resources to enhance teacher-student interaction and teaching results.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Requirement 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="h-16 w-16 bg-purple-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-4">New Challenges of Hybrid Education</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">The hybrid education mode of online and offline courses puts forward higher requirements for students' participation and learning effectiveness.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What UNV Offers Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-white">What UNV Offers</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-center text-gray-300 mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          In today's society, education departments in many countries have decided to intelligentize and digitize classrooms to meet the growing demand for teaching.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Solution 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <div class="relative h-48">
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517502884422-41eaead166d4?ixlib=rb-4.0.3" 
                alt="Interactive Teaching Display" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">New Era of Teacher-Student Interaction</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">The InstaHub series has extraordinary audio-visual performance and is compatible with various educational software resources.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Solution 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <div class="relative h-48">
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555212697-194d092e3b8f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3" 
                alt="Touch Interface" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Touching the Future</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">The touchscreen makes it fluent to write, modify and save. Available in 65/75/86 inches for different classroom spaces.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Solution 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <div class="relative h-48">
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558008258-3256797b43f3?ixlib=rb-4.0.3" 
                alt="Modern Classroom" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Simplified Classroom Space</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Replace multiple equipment with a single integrated solution, bringing classroom space back to simplicity.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Success Cases Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16">Success Cases</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Case 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="relative h-64">
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523050854058-8df90110c9f1?ixlib=rb-4.0.3" 
                alt="Al-Amal International School"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6">
                <span class="text-white text-sm font-medium bg-blue-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Education</span>
                <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mt-2">Al-Amal International School, Yemen</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Al-Amal International School, established in 1997, is focused on the Kg-Primary-Secondary education in Yemen.</p>
              <a href="/cases/al-amal-school" class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-700">
                Read More
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>